---
import Link from "../atoms/Link.astro";
import StoryImage from "../molecules/StoryImage.astro";
import Byline from "../molecules/Byline.astro";
import Interaction from "../molecules/Interaction.astro";
---

<header class="flow article-top">
  <div>
    <div class="flex-row">
      <Link href="/" text="Finans" classes="category" />

      <ul role="list" class="info">
        <li>01. mars 2023</li>
        <li>|</li>
        <li>2 min</li>
        <li>|</li>
        <li><Link href="/" text="Paid" classes="tag" /></li>
      </ul>
</div>
  </div>
    <h1>
      Ny konkursbølge under oppseiling: – Nå blir det verre
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Konkurstallene stiger mot nye høyder. Så langt i år er antall konkurser innen detaljhandel og hotell/restaurant blitt mer enn doblet sammenlignet med i fjor.
    </p>
  </div>
  <StoryImage />
  <Byline />
  <Interaction />
</header>

<style>
  header {
    align-items: flex-start;
    color: var(--color-text-typo, currentColor);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block-start: var(--hero-top-space, 1.75rem);
    max-width: var(--grid-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .flex-row{
    display: flex;

  }

  ul[role="list"] {
    inline-size: min(
      var(--grid-width),
      100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
    );
    margin-block-end: .7rem;
    padding-inline-start: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--typography-ui-font-family);

    &.info{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      column-gap: 1rem;
      color: #53585F;
    }
  }

  div {
    display: grid;
    grid-area: a;
    padding-block-start:1.75rem;
    row-gap: 0.5rem;

    & > * {
      inline-size: min(
        var(--grid-width),
        100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
      );
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--hero-font, "SmBold23", sans-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
        inline-size: min(
      var(--grid-width),
      100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
    );


    @media (--medium) {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  p.lead {
    font-size: 1.6rem !important;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    padding-block-start: 1rem;
    padding-block-end: 1rem;
        inline-size: min(
      var(--grid-width),
      100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
    );
  }
</style>
